reviewText: This product was just a repeat of the other movies I have about the royal couple, William & Kate, just condensed into a few less discs.
A great addition to our DVD collections.  Alway fun to have history DVD's that can be share with younger generations to come.

on 3 DVDs you get same photos and short video files over and over again.  More people talking empty talks.  Really waisted money and time.  I was always %100 satisfied with Amazon products, however this purchase really disappointed me.

It would seem after waiting for weeks to receive this and view, it would be outstanding.  But a huge disappointment was in store.  Lots of repitition and very few new or interesting stories about Kate and Wills.  The biggest disappointment of all......NOTHING of the actual wedding.  How can you title the DVD 'Royal Wedding' without including any real footage of the wedding.  Unbelievable!!

THERE ARE NO PHOTOS OF KATE AND WILLIAM'S WEDDING ON ANY OF THE 3 DVD'S INCLUDED IN THIS SERIES! I ordered this thinking to have photos of this royal wedding, however, the only wedding photos are of Charles and Diana's wedding and other royalty pairs. While there are a lot of good photos of both Catherine and William from childhood on through their courtship and school days, it is a huge disappointment not to have their wedding included.  The material is worthwhile, but the title is certainly misleading.  I would not have purchased this series if I had known the wedding was not on any of the DVD's.
I didn't get to see the wedding as I live on the West Coast so it was such a pleasure to sit down and take it all in.  Really fun to watch!
